# Scoped to examples/live-capstone/Dockerfile ONLY (BuildKit reads `<dockerfile>.dockerignore` next to
# the Dockerfile before the repo-root .dockerignore). Keeps this image's repo-root build context lean
# WITHOUT changing the root app image's context — same convention as benchmarks/Dockerfile.dockerignore.
# The image installs deps and builds the bundle fresh, so local installs/build artifacts must never ship.
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
var
coverage
**/coverage
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
.next
**/.next
.svelte-kit
**/.svelte-kit
.claude
.playwright-mcp
.devcontainer
*.png
